    <title>Blog Notes</title>
    <url>/Displace.github.io/2024/05/08/2/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>My brain’s getting worse, so let’s just write it down here</p>
<h2 id="Quick-Start"><a href="#Quick-Start" class="headerlink" title="Quick Start"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id="Preview-and-upload"><a href="#Preview-and-upload" class="headerlink" title="Preview and upload"></a>Preview and upload</h3><div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Bash"><figure class="iseeu highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s             preview</span><br><span class="line">hexo g -d          upload</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<p>Preview: <a class="link" href="http://localhost:4000/Displace.github.io/">local preview  <i class="fa-regular fa-arrow-up-right-from-square fa-sm"></i></a></p>
<p>Upload: <a class="link" href="https://github.com/MikumikuDAIFans/Displace.github.io">GitHub Warehouse <i class="fa-regular fa-arrow-up-right-from-square fa-sm"></i></a></p>
<h3 id="Document-location"><a href="#Document-location" class="headerlink" title="Document location"></a>Document location</h3><div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Bash"><figure class="iseeu highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">articles Location: D:\My_Boke\Blog_Redefine\<span class="built_in">source</span>\_posts</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pictures location(<span class="built_in">local</span>): D:\My_Boke\Blog_Redefine\themes\redefine\<span class="built_in">source</span>\images  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pictures location(will be upload): D:\My_Boke\Blog_Redefine\.deploy_git\images  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
]]></content>
